Additionally, the paper discusses the practical applications of their proposed model, which could fall under the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). Finally, the paper discusses the use of categorical relevance levels, which could fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
